y's race\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"uncertainty\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an embarrassing blow to Olympics organisers, the men's race has been postponed to immediately after the women's event on Wednesday, which is scheduled for 8am.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an embarrassing blow\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics organisers\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's race\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's event\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"8am\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both events will be subject to testing.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both events\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"testing\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 officials remain confident that water quality levels will eventually improve to safely swim in the Seine - afterspending around \\u20ac1.5bn to clean up the riverfor the Olympics - but there are further contigency plans in place if they do not.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9647067616570485e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999752163, \"rank\": 2.4719075982527702e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"water quality levels\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverfor\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"further contigency plans\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there are storm warnings on Tuesday night and rain forecast on Wednesday, with levels of pollution and harmful bacteria including E.coli in the Seine linked to the weather.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999752163, \"rank\": 2.4719075982527702e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"storm warnings\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday night and rain forecast\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"levels\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"pollution and harmful bacteria\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"E.coli\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A statement said from Paris 2024 and World Triathlon said: \\\"The tests carried out in the Seine today revealed water quality levels that did not provide sufficient guarantees to allow the event to be held.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0073051390527304e-18, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1